data.description: Wonderful family home with 4 bedrooms 2.5 baths, open floor plan, a bonus space that could be an office or playroom on main level. Laminate and ceramic tile on main level with hardwood flooring in powder room. All bedrooms and full bathrooms upstairs, as well as the laundry room.  2 car garage.  Large open kitchen with center island overlooking backyard.  Located in cul-de-sac with a huge backyard to entertain friends and family as well as in a community with a pool and playground.
